PDI_PLUGIN(example)
 If user create specification tree: data:
some_integer:int

plugins:
example:~
 And a program: #include<pdi.h>

intmain()
{
PDI_init(PC_parse_path("spec_tree.yaml"));
intsome_integer=0;
PDI_expose("some_integer",&some_integer,PDI_OUT);
PDI_finalize();
return0;
}
 The console will display: [PDI][13:42:41]***info:Initializationsuccessful
Userhassharedadatanamedsome_integer
